# RDX Revamp Governance

This repo is in a **planned repositioning**. Implementation must follow `docs/`.

## Before coding

1. Read `docs/README.md` for active phase
2. Read `docs/RDX_Scope_Boundaries.md` for that phase only
3. Read `docs/RDX_File_Ownership_Map.md`

State phase + files to touch + files to avoid at session start.

## Hard stops

- No work outside active phase
- No deleting legacy routes/API without phase approval
- No invented metrics or fake testimonials (see Content Copy Bank)
- No new npm packages without founder OK
- No mass refactors of `src/data/` or legacy components

## New code goes here

- `src/components/rdx/`
- `src/content/rdx/`
- `src/styles/rdx/tokens.css`

## End of session

Run `npm run build` and `npm run lint`. Update phase checklist if items completed.

Skills: `.agents/skills/rdx-revamp/` + `.agents/skills/hallmark/` for design.
